{
  "title": "Light Umami Norwegian Biscuits Salad",
  "description": "A refreshing, dairyfree postworkout salad that blends crisp oatbased cookie crumbs with salmon, avocado, and an umami dressing.",
  "cuisine": "Norwegian",
  "diet": [
