  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a small skillet over medium heat and toast the biscuits until golden brown, about 2 minutes.",
    "Transfer the toasted biscuits to a bowl and crush them into fine crumbs using a rolling pin or your hands.",
    "In a separate small bowl, whisk together soy sauce, miso paste, rice vinegar, lime juice, olive oil, salt, and pepper until well blended.",
    "Add the arugula to the bowl of dressing and toss until the leaves are evenly coated.",
    "Fold in the crumbled biscuits, diced salmon, avocado, and toasted sesame seeds, mixing gently to keep the avocado from breaking apart.",
    "Taste and adjust seasoning if necessary.",
    "Serve immediately for a crunchy, light, umami\u2011packed snack."
  ],
